Shawnae Nicole Jebbia (amụrụ na Septemba 13, n'afọ 1971) bụ onye America na-eme egwuregwu na onye na-ahụ maka ịma mma nke meriri Miss USA n'afọ 1998.

Jebbia meriri Miss Massachusetts USA n'afọ 1997, na mbọ mbụ ya na asọmupi.   Ọ gara n'ihu na-anọchite anya Massachusetts na asọmupi Miss USA 1998, bụrụ onye mmeri Miss USA mbụ nke steeti ahụ.  Ọ bụ ezie na Jebbia enwechaghị ahụmahụ tupu oge ahụ, onye mbụ ya bụ Shauna Gambill nweburu aha Miss Teen USA 1994
Jebbia's "sister" titleholder, Miss Massachusetts Teen USA 1998 Susie Castillo, gara n'ihu jide Miss Massachusetts USA title wee bụrụ Massachusetts's second Miss USA titleholder na 2003.
Jebbia sonyere na asọmupi Miss Universe 1998 mgbe afọ ahụ gasịrị

Akara dị elu na uwe mgbede na asọmupi uwe igwu mmiri mere ka ọ gaa na 5 ikpeazụ mana mgbe ajụjụ ọnụ ahụ gasịrị, o meghị nke ikpeazụ 3 ikpeazụ.  Onye meriri bụ Wendy Fitzwilliam nke Trinidad na Tobago, onye Jebbia biri ma pụta n'oge ọchịchị ya.

Jebbia tolitere na Sonoma County, California ma biri na Sebastopol, California ruo afọ isii.  O nwetara nzere na nkwukọrịta na Mahadum Jacksonville ma gụsịrị akwụkwọ cum laude na agụmakwụkwọ egwuregwu.  Ọ pụtara na telivishọn na ihe nkiri, gụnyere ịbụ "Barker Beauty" na The Price Is Right site na afo 2002 wee ruo n'afọ 2003 na oge na mmemme mmega ahụ ESPN2 Co-ed Training tupu o merie Miss USA. Mgbe ọrịa Ménière kpatara nsogbu ntị, Jebbia si na ụlọ ọrụ ntụrụndụ pụọ ma na-agụ akwụkwọ ugbu a maka nzere masta na nọọsụ.  Ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka ọnụ na-ekwuru Siemens Pure 700 hearing aid.
